      "content": "but that's the thing... it's not just a \"feeling.\" i look at the people i owe, the people who believed in me, and i just feel like there is no path back from this. there's no version of the future where this isn't just a constant, heavy stain on my life. it feels like the only honest thing to do is just stop. to just stop having to face this every single second. everything feels so final.",
